OL,3,CGrandmother diagnosed with blood
OL,4,Cdisease she didn't know she had after
OL,5,Cnew test
OL,7,FA grandmother from Birmingham has told
OL,8,FITV News she would never have known
OL,9,Fshe was living with Hepatitis B if it
OL,10,Fwasn't for an opt-out testing scheme
OL,11,Ffor blood-borne viruses.
OL,13,FSuffering from stomach pains, Renuka
OL,14,FChandan, 71, went to the Queen
OL,15,FElizabeth Hospital in Birmingham.
OL,17,FShe was diagnosed with gallstones and,
OL,18,Fshockingly, Hepatitis B - a blood-
OL,19,Fborne virus that can lead to serious
OL,20,Fliver damage and even cancer.
