OL,7,FFrom Tuesday 18 March, every patient
OL,8,Faged 16 and over who visits the A&E at
OL,9,FHeartlands and Good Hope Hospitals
OL,10,Fwill automatically be tested for these
OL,11,Finfections if they're already having
OL,12,Fblood taken - unless they choose to
OL,13,Fopt out.
