OL,7,FThis expansion builds on the scheme's
OL,8,Fsuccess at the Queen Elizabeth
OL,9,FHospital, which introduced the
OL,10,Fapproach on 3 September last year. In
OL,11,Fjust over six months, more than 22,500
OL,12,Ftests have been carried out there,
OL,13,Fleading to 36 new diagnoses -
OL,14,Fincluding four cases of HIV, 19 of
OL,15,Fhepatitis B, and 13 of hepatitis C.
OL,17,FEven more significantly, 55 people
OL,18,Fdiagnosed previously but not receiving
OL,19,Ftreatment were identified and
OL,20,Freconnected with care.
