OL,7,FDr Steve Taylor, Lead HIV Consultant
OL,8,Fat Birmingham Heartlands Hospital and
OL,9,FClinical Director for the Birmingham
OL,10,FFast Track Cities initiative, welcomed
OL,11,Fthe move:
OL,13,F"We've already seen fantastic results
OL,14,Ffrom this programme here in
OL,15,FBirmingham. This is a game-changer for
OL,16,Four city."
OL,18,FHe emphasised the importance of early
OL,19,Fdiagnosis:
