OL,7,F"HIV, hepatitis B, and hepatitis C can
OL,8,Fgo undetected for years, causing
OL,9,Fserious harm before symptoms even
OL,10,Fappear. But with today's treatments,
OL,11,FHIV and hepatitis B can be managed for
OL,12,Flife, and hepatitis C can actually be
OL,13,Fcured.
OL,15,F"Diagnosing these infections early
OL,16,Fsaves lives and prevents further
OL,17,Ftransmission."
