OL,7,F"This has taken immense dedication
OL,8,Ffrom teams across our laboratories,
OL,9,Fvirology, and emergency departments.
OL,10,FTheir commitment to public health and
OL,11,Ftackling these infections head-on is
OL,12,Fnothing short of extraordinary."
OL,14,FAll test results are kept strictly
OL,15,Fconfidential and handled by specialist
OL,16,Fhealthcare professionals. Patients
OL,17,Fwon't need to do anything extra - if
OL,18,Fthey're having blood taken anyway,
OL,19,Fthey'll be tested unless they actively
OL,20,Fopt-out.
